ne\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"string\">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"keyword\">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">const</span> <span class=\"type\">int</span> N = <span class=\"number\">1e5</span> + <span class=\"number\">10</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title class_\">node</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> to, nxt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">} a[N], b[N];</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> pre[N], k, dfn[N], low[N], n, m, x, y, dp[N], inst[N], id[N], si[N], v[N], vD[N];</span><br><span class=\"line\">stack&lt;<span class=\"type\">int</span>&gt; st;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> times, sccnt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">tarjan</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> x)</span> </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    inst[x] = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    dfn[x] = low[x] = ++times;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    st.<span class=\"built_in\">push</span>(x);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"type\">int</span> i = pre[x]; i; i = a[i].nxt) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (!dfn[a[i].to]) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">tarjan</span>(a[i].to);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            low[x] = <span class=\"built_in\">min</span>(low[x], low[a[i].to]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        } <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (inst[a[i].to]) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">            low[x] = <span class=\"built_in\">min</span>(low[x], dfn[a[i].to]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (dfn[x] == low[x]) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"type\">int</span> t;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        sccnt++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">do</span> {</span><br><span class=\"line\">            t = st.<span class=\"built_in\">top</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            st.<span class=\"built_in\">pop</span>();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            inst[t] = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            id[t] = sccnt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            si[sccnt]++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            vD[sccnt] += v[t];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        } <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> (t != x);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">add</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> u, <span class=\"type\">int</span> v)</span> </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    a[++k] = {v, pre[u]};</span><br><span class=\"line\">    pre[u] = k;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> preD[N], kb;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">addD</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> u, <span class=\"type\">int</span> v)</span> </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    b[++kb] = {v, preD[u]};</span><br><span class=\"line\">    preD[u] = kb;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span> </span>{</span><br><span class=\"line\">    cin &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"type\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i++) cin &gt;&gt; v[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"type\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i &lt;= m; i++) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        cin &gt;&gt; x &gt;&gt; y;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">add</span>(x, y);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"type\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i++) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (!dfn[i])</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">tarjan</span>(i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"type\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i++) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"type\">int</span> j = pre[i]; j; j = a[j].nxt) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"type\">int</span> x = id[i], y = id[a[j].to];</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (x != y) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"built_in\">addD</span>(x, y);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            }</span><br><span class=\"line\">        }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"type\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i &lt;= sccnt; i++) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        dp[i] = vD[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> ans = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"type\">int</span> i = sccnt; i &gt;= <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i--) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"type\">int</span> j = preD[i]; j; j = b[j].nxt) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">            dp[b[j].to] = <span class=\"built_in\">max</span>(dp[b[j].to], dp[i] + vD[b[j].to]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"type\">int</span> i = sccnt; i &gt;= <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i--) {</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ans = <span class=\"built_in\">max</span>(ans, dp[i]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    }</span><br><span class=\"line\">    cout &lt;&lt; ans;</span><br><span class=\"line\">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</p>\n</details>\n<p>———— 2025.07.11 FrankWkd.</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"This is the first day that i heve my own blog.Thanks: Powered By Hexo and Github...","permalink":"/post/Hello-Hexo","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Others","slug":"Others","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Others.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"FrankWkd","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.luogu.com.cn/upload/image_hosting/ofl7t46i.png","link":"/","description":"苦心人、天不负，卧薪尝胆，三千越甲可吞吴。 <br /> @ <b>博客园：FrankWkd</b>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/FrankWkd-Pro","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/frankwkd","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/frankwkd","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"给你的Hexo静态博客部署LateX支持","uid":"dcdcee834f273ccf9b6767caa4fb38f8","slug":"LateX-Settings","date":"2025-07-11T09:54:59.000Z","updated":"2025-07-11T10:28:09.529Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/LateX-Settings.json","cover":[],"text":"给你的Hexo静态博客部署 支持众所周知，hexo搭建的静态博客非常nice，但是对于OIer来说没有LateX公式支持，岂不是美中不足？ 在线编写 插入图片1...","permalink":"/post/LateX-Settings","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":897,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"编辑，建站","slug":"编辑，建站","count":1,"path":"api/categories/编辑，建站.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"LateX","slug":"LateX","count":1,"path":"api/tags/LateX.json"}],"author":{"name":"FrankWkd","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cdn.luogu.com.cn/upload/image_hosting/ofl7t46i.png","link":"/","description":"苦心人、天不负，卧薪尝胆，三千越甲可吞吴。 <br /> @ <b>博客园：FrankWkd</b>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/FrankWkd-Pro"